# isOrthogonalCircle

- _isOrthogonalCircle(c₁, c₂)_

A predicate to decide if the two circles, _c₁_ and _c₂_, are orthogonal.

```
>>> let a = Circle([5 0], 4);
>>> let b = Circle([0 0], 3);
>>> a.isOrthogonalCircle(b)
true
```

